%% Flux publication evenement - source Mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  actor Organizer as Organisateur
  participant Front as Back-office organisateur
  participant Gateway as API Gateway
  participant EventMgmt as Event Management
  participant Catalog as Catalog & Search
  participant Bus as Message Bus
  participant Audit as Admin/Audit futur
  actor Visitor as Visiteur public

  Organizer->>Front: Saisit un brouillon valide
  Front->>Gateway: POST /api/events/drafts/{eventId}/publish
  Gateway->>EventMgmt: Route + contexte auth
  EventMgmt->>EventMgmt: Verifie ownership + regles metier
  EventMgmt->>EventMgmt: Transition DRAFT -> PUBLISHED
  EventMgmt-->>Gateway: 200 + eventId/status/publishedAt
  Gateway-->>Front: Reponse succes

  EventMgmt-)Bus: event.published
  Bus-)Catalog: Consume event.published
  Catalog->>Catalog: Upsert CatalogEventView
  Catalog-->>Catalog: Projection publique disponible
  Bus-)Audit: audit.action.recorded (reserve)

  Visitor->>Gateway: GET /api/catalog/events
  Gateway->>Catalog: Route publique
  Catalog-->>Gateway: Liste evenement publie
  Gateway-->>Visitor: Detail ou liste publique
